        "subject": "LU-8535 lod: check already used OSTs at speed=0",
        "message": "LU-8535 lod: check already used OSTs at speed=0\n\nlod_check_and_reserve_ost() skips a check for already used OST\nwhen speed=0 i.e. at the first round of object allocation.\nEnabling the check unconditionally.\n\nChange-Id: I9359dd0cf0bafbcf3ab327ab5f007016a8fc0189\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Zarochentsev <alexander.zarochentsev@seagate.com>\nSigned-off-by: Rahul Deshmukh <rahul.deshmukh@seagate.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
